<!-- 

============================================================
     LOGIN GATE  CEO gets a one-click button, Staff/Admin 

login
     is hidden behind a small toggle link so credentials are 

never
     visible to anyone who just opens the link.
     

============================================================ 

-->
<div id="loginScreen" class="login-screen">
  <div class="login-card">
    <div class="login-brand">
      <h1>Feedback Intelligence Suite</h1>
      <span>Grocery &amp; Fresho &middot; Multi-Branch 

Operations</span>
    </div>

    <button type="button" class="btn-ceo-login" 

onclick="loginAsCeo()">&#128202; Login as CEO</button>

    <button type="button" class="staff-login-toggle" 

onclick="toggleStaffLoginForm()">Staff / Data Entry 

Login</button>

    <form id="staffLoginForm" class="staff-login-form hidden" 

onsubmit="return attemptAdminLogin(event)">
      <label class="field-label">Username</label>
      <input type="text" id="loginUser" 

autocomplete="username" placeholder="Enter username" 

style="margin-bottom:12px;">
      <label class="field-label">Password</label>
      <input type="password" id="loginPass" 

autocomplete="current-password" placeholder="Enter password">
      <button type="submit" class="btn-staff-

login">Login</button>
      <div id="loginError" class="login-error hidden">Galat 

username ya password. Dobara koshish karen.</div>
    </form>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- 

============================================================
     SNAPSHOT EXPORT MODAL  admin-only: bakes current data 

into a
     ready-to-paste code block so it shows correctly on any 

device
     (e.g. the live Netlify link) without relying on this 

browser's
     local storage.
     

============================================================ 

-->
<div id="snapshotModal" class="snapshot-modal hidden">
  <div class="snapshot-card">
    <h2>&#128230; Export Data Snapshot (Lock into Code)</h2>
    <p>
      Yeh code block neeche generate hua hai, jis main aap ka 

abhi tak ka tamam data
      (Branch 1&ndash;4 + Facebook MPK/HYD) shamil hai. Is 

poore box ko copy kar ke save kar len
      &mdash; jab is file ko Netlify (ya kahin bhi) per 

<i>dobara</i> deploy / update karen, to yeh
      block developer ko bhej den taake wo ise code main 

permanently fix kar de. Is ke baad, jo bhi
      browser per yeh link khulay (CEO sahit), use yeh data 

shuru se hi nazar aaye ga &mdash; localStorage
      ki zaroorat nahi paray gi.
    </p>
    <textarea id="snapshotOutput" readonly 

spellcheck="false"></textarea>
    <div class="snapshot-actions">
      <button class="btn-copy-snap" onclick="copySnapshotCode

()">Copy Code</button>
      <button class="btn-close-snap" 

onclick="closeSnapshotModal()">Close</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

